%N A134111 Powers of 5 written backwards and sorted.
%C A134111 All terms but the first one have initial digit 5.
%t A134111 Sort[FromDigits[Reverse[IntegerDigits[#]]]&/@(5^Range[0,30])] (* _Harvey P. Dale_, May 18 2012 *)
%o A134111 (PARI) A134111_first(n)=my(L=log(10)/log(5)); vecsort([A004086(5^k) | k<-[0..n\/L*L\1]])[1..n] \\ _M. F. Hasler_, Mar 27 2026
